>> time required: 20 minutes
>> course: salsa

Fry @garlic cloves{6} in @olive oil{1%cup} until golden
Remove garlic and fry @corn tortilla{1} until golden 
Remove tortilla and add @arbol chilis{20-30} and @ancho chili{1} to oil
Turn heat off and let chilis steep in oil for several minutes
Blend all ingredients with @salt and @sugar to taste
